## Lemonade Server Development

When Lemonade Server is running, the embedding pipeline is fully operational:

```bash
# Start Lemonade (separate terminal)
lemonade-server serve

# Verify
curl http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health

# Pull required models
lemonade-server pull nomic-embed-text
lemonade-server pull bge-reranker-v2-m3   # needed for Phase 4

# Point u-forge.ai at it
export LEMONADE_URL="http://localhost:8000/api/v1"
```

`EmbeddingManager::try_new_auto(None, None)` reads `LEMONADE_URL`. If the variable
is unset or the server is unreachable, it returns a descriptive error ‚Äî there is no
silent local fallback.

