## Testing

```bash
cargo test                              # All tests (no server required)
cargo test storage                      # Module-specific
cargo test -- --nocapture               # With stdout
RUST_LOG=debug cargo test -- --nocapture  # With debug logging
cargo test test_name -- --exact         # Single test by name
```

### Test conventions

- Every test gets its own `TempDir` ‚Üí `KnowledgeGraph::new(temp_dir.path())`.
- No model downloads in unit tests. Embedding tests use `MockEmbeddingProvider`
  (deterministic fake vectors, defined inline) or skip when `LEMONADE_URL` is unset.
- Schema tests use `TempDir` for storage isolation.
- FTS5 search tests: insert a chunk, call `search_chunks_fts`, assert result.

### CI commands

```bash
cargo fmt --check
cargo clippy -- -D warnings
cargo test
cargo doc --no-deps
cargo run --example cli_demo
```

