## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `openssl-sys` build error | `apt install pkg-config libssl-dev` (Ubuntu) / `brew install openssl` (macOS) |
| `Lemonade Server not available` error | Run `lemonade-server serve` and `export LEMONADE_URL=...` |
| Schema not found | Check `$UFORGE_SCHEMA_DIR`, verify `.json` files exist |
| Dimension mismatch (future sqlite-vec) | Ensure embedding model matches vector column dimensions |
| `database is locked` | Only one writer at a time; check for stale processes holding `knowledge.db` |
| Tests fail after adding SQLite column | Run `cargo test` against a fresh `TempDir` ‚Äî tests never share state |